Ing '''Grand Serail''' ({{lang-ar|السراي الكبير}}; a ausan da muring '''Palacio ning Kapamahalan''' o ''Government Palace'') ing pun tanggapan (''headquarters'') ning [[:en:Prime Minister of Lebanon|Pun Ministru ning Lebanon]]. Atiu king babo ning bunduk-bundukan o talimunduk king kabalenan (''downtown'') ning [[Beirut]], pilang bloque manibat king [[:en:Lebanese Parliament|Parlamento ning Lebanon]]. 
Ing Grand Serail metung yang makasalesayan a gusali, ing pekamaulaga kareng atlung makatikdong ibat king panaun a Ottoman king talimunduk a Serail. Deng aliwa ila reng gusaling Council for Development and Reconstruction ampo ing torreng maki relo ning Hamidiyyeh. 
Megi yang maulaga ing gusaling ini uling kareng tuki-tuki nang papil king kasalesayan manibat aniang 1832<ref name="Solidere">{{Citation  | title = The Grand Serail | newspaper = The Quarterly | pages =  | year = 1998 | date = 1998-09 | url =http://www.lebanon.com/construction/the.quarterly/98/jul-sep/serail.html }}</ref> 

